## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the latest research findings. The information is derived from secondary sources, and while efforts were made to ensure accuracy, the dynamic nature of scientific research means that new data could alter these conclusions. Additionally, individual health conditions and responses to vaccines can vary, which may not be fully captured in this report.

